{"tid":579280,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[大種乞兒] 環保閪為$6.8打千字文追討！","createTime":"2018-03-03T12:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T13:42:51.000Z","uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45f4f60d1e9c20cf1aa4edc0745ef55afb276cd8","tid":579280,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"好乸長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大意係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n有條友排咗嘢入咗$12<br />\n收信發現郵費$5.2<br />\nFree group話明&quot;FREE&quot;<br />\n物主不能有錢落袋<br />\n郵費亦要實報實銷<br />\n所以就開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: purple;\">$6.8的抗爭</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/195231_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F195231_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7270105a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/195302_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F195302_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ee11da70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>[然後開始chur物主拎地址<br />\n話封信要即日打回頭！<br />\n否則第日就要畀埋佢退件嘅$5.2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而物主喺收件後應盡快退返$12！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">佢可能買咗淘寶運費險</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><strong> ]</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">勇者唔怕煩繼續睇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾仲有粒殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/195848_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F195848_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bd7ade12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/195855_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F195855_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=cf901857&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係排呢堆嘢<br />\n而家搞一輪 又出嚟再free</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/195640_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F195640_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8c17cf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好煩咩？唔啱睇自己碌過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/204009_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F204009_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=fc1607ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0092811f486daeac84b783d76772720072e82a9f","tid":579280,"uid":34444,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"做咩要加入啲師奶嘅混戰<br />\n你當呢度babycondom?"},{"pid":"59bbbfddfea851b41bef0758c7ec976eee18fe89","tid":579280,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"答佢一句信封要錢，搭𨋢落樓嗰個時間都計錢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br /